\chapter*{Preface}
\vspace{-1.2cm}
Many electronic systems are interacting with their surroundings. The theme of this 
semester is therefore \textit{Digital and Analog Systems Interacting with the Surroundings}. The level is a 5$^\text{th}$ semester project rated to 15 ECTS-points within Electronics \& IT at Aalborg University.

The target group of the report are supervisors, students and other interested parties within the School of Information and Communication Technology at the The Faculty of Engineering and Science.

